Description: Provides helper functions to access datasets from the
    Metropolitan Transportation Authority (MTA) portion of the New York
    State Open Data platform <https://data.ny.gov/>. Returns results as
    tidy tibbles with support for optional filtering, sorting, and row
    limits through the Socrata API.
